{
  "stem": "2002.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I figured out in my mind, in Olyka was the KGB, the Russians.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I said to my brother Srulke, I'm gonna go to stay where the Russians are, even at nighttime, in the area.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When I see them packing and goin' on a truck-- because that's the only way they could leave-- it was a very tiny town-- and then knows that the the Germans are not far away, if they are packing to leave.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So my brother Srulke was gonna go with me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But my other brother and sisters didn't let him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I went alone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That's where it started out to go to-- from no more to Brest-Litovsk, but to go to the Russian border-- to go to Russia.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that started out with the-- with the Ukrainians attacking.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that's where I met my friend.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Now I got to-- to I'm going back and forward now, and I'm going to that we lined up in Kiev.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "About what time?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "This is now 1940?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in 1940.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When did Hitler start-- I forgot when Hitler started the war against Russia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was 1940 or '41, I think.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was after which Stalin thought he's got peace with Hitler.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But Hitler attacked Russia anyways.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we find Kiev.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in Kiev there was a flea market.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I remember taking off my jacket and go to the flea market.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so in the flea market.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm running away from Olyka.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I told this story going from Olyka, which it means, where the plane came down, and where that first was when I went to get that loaf of bread.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when the Ukraines chased me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then I went to, I stayed with the Czechoslovakian.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then I left.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
